    "translation":{"eng":"Illuminating the seven islands of the world, Śrī Navadvīpa-purī shines due to the presence of that king among the gods, Śrī Viśvambhara. There, in the midst of Śrī Viśvambhara’s bhaktas, is the renowned Śrīvāsa Paṇḍita, whose life’s mission is śrī-kṛṣṇa-kīrtana."}},{
