    "translation":{"eng":"Exclusively fixed in the sevā of Gaurāṅga, he does not know any demigod or goddess. Along with his four brothers, servants, and maidservants, he always revels in kīrtana—day and night—with Gaurāṅga and His devotees, intoxicated by prema."}},{
