    "translation":{"eng":"His wife, Śrī Mālinī-devī, whom Mahāprabhu calls ‘Mother,’ is the crown-jewel of all chaste women. Nityānanda Prabhu resides in their house, and she loves Him as her own son. When she sees Nityānanda Prabhu, milk flows from her breasts and tears fall from her eyes."}},{
